commit.message:
Merge branch 'development-serge'

* development-serge:
  Fall detector runs in background as a worker
  Better values for thresholds
  Got relatively ok threshold values
  Seperated accelorometer logic to different files
  Seperated custom sqrt function into its own header
  Added barebones accelorometer detection

Conflicts:
	src/main.c
Fall detector runs in background as a worker

Merge branch 'development-max' into development-martin

* development-max:
  add location and notification services
Seperated accelorometer logic to different files
Communication between Pebble Watch and JS app.

Encapsulated the UI code

- new files pebbletrek_ui.c and pebbletrek_ui.h
- only init() and deinit() are exported to main.c

Added main UI

- fall detected page (s_interrupt_window)
- 15 seconds (or specified) time to countdown for user-action cancel (s_countdown_window)
- emergency mode activated and pinged phone to send SMS (s_sending_window)
Seperated custom sqrt function into its own header

Inition src commit

- Added main.c with basic app init and deinit
- and window load and unload
